{"tid":1586990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[乘勢追擊] 發起 928 九龍塘大遊行 // 929 全港商場大和理shop","createTime":"2019-09-22T08:26:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T10:04:17.000Z","uid":49312,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9c6865223a88d5be28be4c13761944f7b67381a6","tid":1586990,"uid":49312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T08:26:56.000Z","msg":"今個禮拜嘅抗爭，我哋見到新模式<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一日勇一日和<br />\n一日行一日企<br />\n一日前進，一日留守</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一日街頭，一日商場</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個模式有利於我哋拉長抗爭。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家都心知肚明，<br />\n今次抗爭不能停下，一停就係清算換血<br />\n但亦好難兩日都街頭抗爭<br />\n成本好高。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">既然係咁，何不每週一動一靜。<br />\n不斷重複，直到成功。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n往後嘅禮拜，我哋建立一套基本模式<br />\n如果冇其他行動，該禮拜就沿用模式<br />\n每週對整個社會施壓。<br />\n<br />\n只要政府一日唔回應五大訴求<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我哋就永不停止行動<br />\n一刻都唔俾社會回歸平靜</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">街頭運動，商場抗爭<br />\n唔回應，就要香港經濟攬炒陪葬</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"feda22b28ed4e0ffc7c490f6d61110906c0d600b","tid":1586990,"uid":49312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T08:27:24.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"768aaefb585989b6d2b6c631d1e3df5c81a48bdb","tid":1586990,"uid":49312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T08:27:37.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"1fdd587f677a18bc4e8a7a71a7860a5d2d1d9c37","tid":1586990,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T08:27:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=ht